root.title: Tokyo Ants
root.author: Kano Yasuhiro
root.synopsis: A collection of oneshots:1) Tokyo Ants -A special security group consisting of highly-skilled people rescues a hostage.2-3) Enma 1 & 2 -Two different stories about people who can see electricity when someone tells a lie.4) Butterfly: Swallow Tail -About a boy who can see swallowtail butterflies around people who are going to die.
